snippet.title: FM modulation in Simulink 2017 (How to generate FM Modulation using Simulink Tutorial)
snippet.description:
FM modulation in Simulink 2017 (How to generate FM Modulation using Simulink) Uniformedia

In telecommunications and signal processing, frequency modulation (FM) is the encoding of information in a carrier wave by varying the instantaneous frequency of the wave. This contrasts with amplitude modulation, in which the amplitude of the carrier wave varies, while the frequency remains constant.

Download FM modulation model in Simulink: http://onlineengineers.info
(Free Electrical Engineering video lectures, free Online Electrical Engineering courses, Video Tutorials, University Courses, Youtube, Lecture notes.)

What is FM modulation: http://www.radio-electronics.com/info/rf-technology-design/fm-frequency-modulation/what-is-fm-tutorial.php

Check this MATLAB channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgdHSFcXvkN6O3NXvif0-pA
